    "Descrição": "<p>\n<br>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/1_FALLING_SHIPS_TRANS-fdf94.png\">&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nAfter a mysterious force starts pulling spaceships out of the sky, death and destruction rain down on the frontier mining planet of Wolf Prime, littering its surface with wreckage, debris, and danger.&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nTake on the role of Squig, a Wolf Prime denizen and shipyard worker who, with the help of his friend Norton, gathers a team of survivors to embark on a journey that will uncover the mystery behind the sudden cataclysm. Do you have what it takes to save the planet from destruction?&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n<video muted=\"\" loop=\"\" preload=\"auto\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" style=\"margin: auto;display:block;width:100%\"><source src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/ChainLightning_Combat-2d-2e-2d-gif-2e-gif-b4a1f.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nEngage in party-based turn-based combat, plan out each turn to optimize character’s abilities and defeat powerful enemies.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Strategically position your team members on the battlefield, where your choice of characters can significantly impact your chances of success.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Outsmart enemies by moving around the grid, find or make cover, or stay open and get a better vantage on your opponent.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Play cards! Inflict noxious status effects on your enemies and set up party combos to eliminate them.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n<br>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/3_ONE_DECK_TRANS-b0e13.png\">&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n<video muted=\"\" loop=\"\" preload=\"auto\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" style=\"margin: auto;display:block;width:100%\"><source src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/shockingclaw_poisongrenadeupgrade-2d-2e-2d-gif-2e-gif-6f57c.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nCustomize your deck using the branching card upgrade system to unlock new strategies and synergies.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Craft new cards for your heroes with resources you collect during the campaign.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Tailor your character’s decks to work with each other, or make each character unique; the choice is yours.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Upgrade your cards to perfect your strategy and build unstoppable decks.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n<br>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/4_FOUR_SPECIES_TRANS__1_-bbd00.png\">&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/Dialog_5-9d205.png\">&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nWolf Prime is a magnet for species from all over the known galaxy, each of whom comes to the planet for their own reasons, and each of whom will play a part in the story.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Meet a vibrant array of characters. Their personalities range from stoic and solemn to buoyant and whimsical, but all are deeply committed to saving their adopted homeworld.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Learn about the various factions vying for power on Wolf Prime: the Outworld Collective, the Mining Guild, the government of Moros… and the Runshaka death cult, of course.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Get to know the backstories of individual characters through engaging dialogue and compelling cutscenes.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n<br>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/5_ANCIENT_DARKNESS_TRANS-d936c.png\">&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\n<video muted=\"\" loop=\"\" preload=\"auto\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" style=\"margin: auto;display:block;width:100%\"><source src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/Multipe_Biomes_walking-2d-2e-2d-gif-2e-gif-f83a1.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nWhen the ships start crashing around you, survival mode kicks in. But falling wreckage isn’t your only problem.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Take on beasts, bots, and brigands determined to stop you from achieving your missions.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Delve into the lore of an extinct alien species and their age-old enemies.&nbsp;<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li>Uncover the cause of the catastrophe and save Wolf Prime from annihilation.<br>\n&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n<a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/rc8QSGeNKe\"><img src=\"https://items.gog.com/dark_sky/6_DISCORD_TRANS-a0abc.png\"></a>\n</p>",
