    "Nome": "Gunslugs 2",
    "Nome de classificação": "Gunslugs 02",
    "Classificação indicativa": "PEGI 12",
    "Categorias": "",
    "Descrição": "<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://items.gog.com/gunslugs_2/gs2_gog_image-29ca4.png\">\n<br>\n\n<br>\nStep into the boots of the Gunslugs, an elite band of action junkies ready to blow things up, dodge an impossible barrage of bullets, and take on an entire army with nothing but sheer firepower and grit. This isn’t just war—it’s an explosive, adrenaline-fueled, side-scrolling thrill ride packed with over-the-top mayhem, massive explosions, and a never-ending barrage of enemies.  \n<br>\n\n<br>\n<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://items.gog.com/gunslugs_2/gs2_gog_story-76762.png\">\n<br>\n\n<br>\nThe world is under siege. <strong>The Black Duck Army</strong> has returned, and this time, they’re not just aiming for domination—they’re taking their war to the stars! Armed with alien technology and an army of merciless minions, their signal towers spread fear across the planet. But where there’s chaos, there’s a hero. And that hero is <strong>YOU</strong>.  \n<br>\n\n<br>\n<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://items.gog.com/gunslugs_2/gs2_gog_image2-40929.png\">\n<br>\n\n<br>\nFrom train crashes to alien warships, from flamethrowers to lightning guns, <strong>Gunslugs 2</strong> is a non-stop tribute to the glorious excess of classic action flicks from the 80s and 90s. The fate of the galaxy is in your hands—lock and load!  \n<br>\n\n<br>\n<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://items.gog.com/gunslugs_2/gs2_gog_content-0b095.png\">\n<br>\n\n<br>\n<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Seven Deadly Worlds</strong> – Blast your way through seven unique, action-packed environments with eight intense levels each.  </li><li><strong>Non-Stop Mayhem</strong> – Battle against tanks, helicopters, giant robots, and alien invaders in a relentless war zone.  </li><li><strong>Explosive Boss Battles</strong> – Face off against monstrous war machines and Black Duck commanders at the end of every level.  </li><li><strong>Weapons Galore</strong> – Wield everything from classic rocket launchers to high-tech lightning guns.  </li><li><strong>Procedurally Generated Chaos</strong> – No two runs are the same with randomly generated enemy bases and inside areas.  </li><li><strong>Cinematic Pixel Carnage</strong> – Experience dynamic cutscenes that bring the battle to life.  </li><li><strong>Retro Vibes, Modern Mayhem</strong> – Inspired by the best of 80s and 90s action movies, with a pixel-art style that brings the chaos to life.  </li></ul>\n<br>\nPrepare for a bullet storm like no other— <strong>Gunslugs 2</strong> is here, and it's time to go out with a bang!\n<br>\n\n<br>\n<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://items.gog.com/gunslugs_2/gunslugs_logo-a9f8a.gif\">",
