    "Descrição": "Garrett, the Master Thief, steps out of the shadows into the City. In this treacherous place, where the Baron’s Watch spreads a rising tide of fear and oppression, his skills are the only things he can trust. Even the most cautious citizens and their best-guarded possessions are not safe from his reach.\n<br><br>\nAs an uprising emerges, Garrett finds himself entangled in growing layers of conflict. Lead by Orion, the voice of the people, the tyrannized citizens will do everything they can to claim back the City from the Baron’s grasp. The revolution is inevitable. If Garrett doesn’t get involved, the streets will run red with blood and the City will tear itself apart.\n<br><br>Garrett never paid the price for anything… until now.\n<br><br>\nTHIEF: Definitive Edition includes the complete base game as well as the following bonus content\n<ul>\n<li>The Bank Heist bonus mission\n</li><li>The Forsaken challenge map\n</li><li>Booster Pack DLC – Opportunist\n</li><li>Booster Pack DLC – Predator\n</li><li>Booster Pack DLC – Ghost\n</li><li><i>Thief: Tales From The City</i> digital comic (EN/FR) & OST\n</li>\n</ul>",
