    "Nome": "Wild Country",
    "Nome de classificação": "",
    "Classificação indicativa": "",
    "Categorias": "",
    "Descrição": "<p>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/w2wcban-c8914.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<video muted loop preload=\"auto\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" style=\"margin: auto;display:block;width:100%\"><source src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/intro_trailer_cinematic_gog-2d-2d-2d-ezgif-2d-2e-2d-com-2d-2d-2d-optimize-2e-gif-60106.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nWILD COUNTRY is a fantastical strategy game where players use beautifully illustrated cards to construct buildings and perform abilities to build the best city. Buildings score points, and the first to reach the objective wins!\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nWild Country combines CCG gameplay with innovative mechanics inspired by classic city-building games to create something unique and approachable. This game is for people looking for something wholesome, comedic, strategic, and full of things to do.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nDo you have what it takes to win?\n</p>\n<h4>Feature Overview</h4>\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n<ul>\n\t<li>Build your deck of 30 cards. Each card represents a Building, Ability, or Event with a unique action. The goal of the game is to outsmart and outearn your rival.</li>\n\t<li>Play cards to place buildings and earn enough profit, but remember that placing certain building types next to one another can have positive (or negative) effects.</li>\n\t<li>There is always something new to collect, learn, and master. There’s a deck for every personality and playstyle, and it’s up to you to discover your winning strategy.</li>\n\t<li>Grow your collection and stand out from the crowd! There’s a ton to customize, from mayors, skins, and outfits to flags, emotes, and cards.</li>\n\t<li>Embark on a journey like no other! Advance through a campaign bursting with mysteries to discover, quests to uncover, and things to do.</li>\n\t<li>Grab your friends to join the chaos with competitive and casual game modes!</li>\n\t<li>Don’t be afraid if you’re new to the genre! Anyone can join the fun with intuitive mechanics and customizable gameplay options to suit your needs.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/cosy__2_-e8d8a.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nCompete against rival competitors in a battle to build the best city. Watch out for earthquakes, snowstorms, and rebellious raccoons. Unpredictable events test your resolve or turn the tide of battle.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nWhether new to card games or a seasoned fan, Wild Country offers endless replayability, strategic gameplay, and unpredictable mischief.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<video muted loop preload=\"auto\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" style=\"margin: auto;display:block;width:100%\"><source src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/bomb2-2e-gif-10e04.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/custom-05bbb.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nThere is always something new to collect, learn, and master. There’s a deck for every personality and playstyle, and it’s up to you to find the cards for your winning strategy.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nSelect and customize from a wild cast of characters, each with their own personalities.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/custom1-5fea1.gif\">\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/explore-743cd.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nEmbark on a journey like no other and complete Wild Country’s expansive story campaign.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nExplore Big Sky Canyon, an idyllic region scattered with a colorful cast of characters. Some think you’re cool, some are determined to beat you, and others might be from the future.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nCollect cards, discover mysteries, and battle other competitors in the single-player campaign... Or just enjoy the view.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<video muted loop preload=\"auto\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" style=\"margin: auto;display:block;width:100%\"><source src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/talk1-2e-gif-8a60f.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/online-f01f9.png\">\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nTake your cards online and compete in both casual and ranked matches!\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nMake friends, make rivals, make profit, and have fun!\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<video muted loop preload=\"auto\" autoplay=\"autoplay\" style=\"margin: auto;display:block;width:100%\"><source src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/onlinecards-2e-gif-85708.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video>\n</p>\n<h4>NO EXPERIENCE NECESSARY</h4>\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nNever played a CCG or City Builder before? No problem! Wild Country is easy to pick up and play, with plenty of depth for those with the skills.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nAnyone can join the fun with patient mechanics and customizable gameplay to suit your needs. Need extra time? Opponent too difficult? Don’t worry, you can change all that.\n</p>\n<h4>REGULAR UPDATES &amp; EVENTS</h4>\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nRegular updates, events, and limited-time content keep WILD COUNTRY fresh and exciting.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nFree updates containing fixes and improvements, as well as new quests, challenges, and collectible content, help to improve your experience, grow your collection, and keep your claws sharp.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\nThe next update is never too far away.\n</p>\n\n<p>\n&nbsp;\n</p>\n\n<p>\n<img src=\"https://items.gog.com/wild_country_1373405737/duck_bottom-5f4d3.png\">\n</p>",
